fixed cost, 𝐹 , variable costs linked to the transactions within the
blockchain, 𝑐𝐵 , and the tokens, 𝑣. While the adoption of a blockchain
activates the effect of the triple (𝐹 , 𝑐𝐵 , 𝑣), it also nullifies the effect
