into higher chances to increase the firm’s economic outcomes.
Note that the business opportunities offered through a smart RSC developed and proposed by blockchain applications leaves the consumers
worse off from an economic point of view. As displayed in Proposition 14, the retailer charges higher prices when a smart RSC is in place,
