not translate into lower sales. This is due to the higher quantity that the
retailer puts in the market, which increases the availability of the goods
to a wider population. Therefore, a compensating effect exists between
quantity availability and service with the pricing strategy that goes in
favor of increasing overall sales under a smart RSC in blockchains.

